", \"from\": 6506, \"to\": 6523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The World Players Associationissued a statementlast week calling for reforms in WADA's process, and the Team USA Athletes' Commission and USA Swimming'' Athletes' Advisory Councilsent a letter to the White Houseasking for an independent investigation of the case.\", \"from\": 6525, \"to\": 6788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6629, \"end\": 6637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999655093420257, \"rank\": 3.449184756934784e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The World Players\", \"from\": 6525, \"to\": 6542}, {\"ngram\": \"a statementlast week\", \"from\": 6561, \"to\": 6581}, {\"ngram\": \"reforms\", \"from\": 6594, \"to\": 6601}, {\"ngram\": \"WADA's process\", \"from\": 6605, \"to\": 6619}, {\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 6709, \"to\": 6717}, {\"ngram\": \"the White Houseasking\", \"from\": 6721, \"to\": 6742}, {\"ngram\": \"an independent investigation\", \"from\": 6747, \"to\": 6775}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 6779, \"to\": 6787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of high-profile swimmers who swam against the Chinese swimmers who tested positive for TMZ have shared their reactions to these revelations - and their support for USADA.\", \"from\": 6790, \"to\": 6969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6845, \"end\": 6852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999895567343244, \"rank\": 1.0422876702503528e-05, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 6886, \"end\": 6889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.820405184735813e-32, \"text\": \"TMZ\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TMZ\", \"dbpedia\